        <abstract> 
<p>Congratulates RC on his work on Scottish sea-margins [<hi rend="italic">Ancient sea-margins</hi> (1848)].</p> 
            <p>Discusses Glen Roy; Milne staggered him in favour of the glacier view, but now his opinion has reverted.</p>
        </abstract>
